              "id": "CVE-2025-9714-libxml2",
              "name": "RpmMatcherExactDirectMatch",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CVE-2025-9714 medium vulnerability for libxml2 package"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "A flaw was found in libxstl/libxml2. The 'exsltDynMapFunction' function in libexslt/dynamic.c does not contain a recursion depth check, which may cause an infinite loop via a specially crafted XSLT document while handling 'dyn:map()', leading to stack exhaustion and a local denial of service."
