              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "A flaw was found in libexpat. A remote attacker could exploit this vulnerability by providing specially crafted Document Type Definition (DTD) content. This could lead to an infinite loop during parsing, resulting in a Denial of Service (DoS) for the application using libexpat."
